data.description: SINGLE STORY, CORNER TOWNHOME - spans the length of the townhouse building. From garage, enter thru courtyard or direct to laundry room/master bedroom. Well appointed living areas with easy to maintain wood laminate and tile in all traffic areas. Carpet in bedrooms. Fireplace in great room style living room and private backyard area. Gated oasis off 95 & Flamingo (Flamingo & Sandhill).
